data.message: Help- I can not get email notifications-I went to settings-notifications and checked ALL -I also checked my spam -nothing -I changed my password and did not get that email. I have an aol account,please help

replies.message: Hi Donna. If you're having issues with email notifications, try these troubleshooting tips: http://bit.ly/2rjvtDb. Hope that helps! -William
I tried all of that yesterday it did not help-I messaged 'report a problem' and have not heard back-please help
I messaged them weeks ago with an issue and no one has responded.   Nothing in the help center is helpful either.  I don't understand why it's so difficult to get help
